Class Customer

    • user_management.User
      • user_management.PhysicalUser

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, PeopleToNotify

    public class Customer
extends PhysicalUser
implements PeopleToNotify, java.io.Serializable
    Implementation of Customer, extends the PhysicalUser class. Implements the PeopleToNotify interface. A customer can receive notifications sent by restaurants thanks to an observer pattern.
    Author:
    maxspahn, jeremyaugot
